                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17160712-3-off15 t17160712-3-crimeloc16"></join> , where the Prisoner was taken; and searching it, found the Libels aforesaid. The Prisoner own'd his Livelihood depended upon felling Pamphlets in that Manner, as his Father did before. The Jury found him <rs id="t17160712-3-verdict17" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17160712-3-verdict17" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
